external_knowledge:
Highly rated medications refer to medications with higher average ratings given by users, indicating better performance or effectiveness of the medication.; 
Medication ratings can range from 1-5, with 5 being the highest rating.; 
More than 10 reviews indicate a relatively large number of user opinions, making the average rating more representative of the medication's quality.

sql:
SELECT name 
FROM medications 
ORDER BY name;

SELECT name, approval_status
FROM medications
ORDER BY approval_status DESC, name ASC;
